    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300049057_14_4531-4596",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "4531-4596",
      "markText": "而令我奇怪的是，摘帽之后，那位给我戴帽的先生好像没事人一样，照样和我寒暄周旋，真称得上“翻手为云覆手雨”, “宰相肚里能撑船”了。",
      "totalCount": 160,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300049057&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=4531&rangeEnd=4596",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ec32ac0813ab79a9g017d96?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=4531&rangeEnd=4596"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300049057_5_2258-2467",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2258-2467",
      "markText": "：一次，我和朱家溍先生去故宫，他开玩笑地对我说：“到君家故宅了。”我连忙纠正道：“不，是到‘君’家故宅了。”因为清朝的紫禁城是接收明朝朱家旧业的。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300049057&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2258&rangeEnd=2467",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ec32ac0813ab79a9g017d96?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2258&rangeEnd=2467"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300049057_11_5178-5234",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "5178-5234",
      "markText": "回忆这五十多年，我总是在“失”中获“得”，使我“得”的固然有恩，使我“失”的实起了促进、激励作用，其恩亦何可泯！",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300049057&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=5178&rangeEnd=5234",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3ec32ac0813ab79a9g017d96?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=5178&rangeEnd=5234"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300049057_10_1182-1268",
